Class TeacherAttendanceSummaryCenterPanel.AttendanceRecord

java.lang.Object
ticktocktrack.gui.TeacherAttendanceSummaryCenterPanel.AttendanceRecord
Enclosing class:
TeacherAttendanceSummaryCenterPanel
public static class TeacherAttendanceSummaryCenterPanel.AttendanceRecord extends Object
Represents an attendance record summary for a student. Contains details about the student's attendance status and totals.
